One Tool - Student Academic Helper
One Tool is a comprehensive web application designed to help students with their academic tasks. It combines multiple productivity tools into a single, easy-to-use interface.

Features
To-Do List: Manage tasks with completion tracking and progress visualization

Calculator: Basic arithmetic operations with a clean interface

Conversion Tool: Convert between different units of length, temperature, and weight

Timer & Stopwatch: Customizable timer and stopwatch functionality

Strategy Timer: Pomodoro and Triangle technique timers for focused study sessions

PDF Notes: Upload and download PDF files for note management

Quote Generator: Motivational quotes to keep you inspired

Calendar & Reminders: Monthly calendar with reminder functionality

Getting Started
Prerequisites
A modern web browser (Chrome, Firefox, Safari, Edge)

No additional installations required
